该节点涉及的全局状态如下：
  - patients (read_write): Dict mapping patient_id to {name, dob, contact, insurance, registered_at}
  - appointments (read_write): Dict mapping appointment_id to {patient_id, doctor_id, time, status, notes}
  - records (read_write): Dict mapping record_id to {patient_id, type, data, created_by, timestamp}

请说明你对每个全局变量的理解。它的数据结构是什么？读写操作分别在什么场景下发生？
